        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">2</span><div><strong>If you smell gas, leave immediately</strong><p>Do not touch any switches. Open windows and doors. Call <a href="https://cadentgas.com/gas-escapes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;">Cadent Gas on 0800 111 999</a> first. Then call us on 07399 676656 once the property is made safe. Our first visit to make a gas escape safe is free.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">3</span><div><strong>For no heating, check boiler pressure</strong><p>If your boiler shows an error code or has cut out, check the pressure gauge. It should read between 1 and 1.5 bar. Below 0.5 bar you can repressurise using the filling loop beneath the boiler. If this does not resolve the fault, call us on 07399 676656.</p></div></div>
